text: Yearinan is an unbounded locality in north-western New South Wales, Australia, within the locality of Bugaldie. A railway station on the closed Gwabegar railway line was located there between 1923 and 1974.Yearinan station NSWrail.net, accessed 9 April 2010. ==References== Category:Localities in New South Wales Category:Warrumbungle Shire
